            <description><![CDATA[<h3>1.0.0-beta.2: Aesthetic & Stability Update</h3>

<p><strong>New Features:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>
    <strong>Ice Migration:</strong> You can now import your old Ice settings,
    including your custom control item positions.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>New Branding:</strong> Full transition to the "Thaw" aesthetic,
    featuring a brand-new app icon.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Better Shortcuts:</strong> Added <code>Command + ,</code> to quickly
    open settings directly from the search window.
  </li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Improvements & Fixes:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>
    <strong>Smarter Hiding:</strong> Enhanced the "Smart Rehide" strategy with
    better focus monitoring and auto-hiding menu bar support.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Reliability:</strong> Improved menu open detection to ensure the
    menu bar behaves predictably.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Cursor Fix:</strong> Resolved an issue where the cursor could
    occasionally stay hidden due to tracking errors.
  </li>
</ul>
]]></description>
